## 4. CSV Export (.csv)

### Purpose
Generate plain-text CSV files for users who need raw tabular data for further processing.

### Library
- Python `csv` stdlib (no extra dependency)

### Output format
- File extension: `.csv`
- Columns: same as Excel export (Batch name, Sample folder name, Compound number, Compound name, U-Del comment, Is U-Del)
- No summary row (summary is Excel-only in v1, or separate CSV file if needed)
- UTF-8 encoding

### Export scope
- Same filtering logic as Excel export (batch selection or full DB)

